{"tid":219821,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你地點解會留意自己另一半?","createTime":"2017-04-27T13:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T09:16:39.000Z","uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81b3702508bbe2861e1da31153727123a6e08991","tid":219821,"uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:12:26.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n大學讀同一科<br />\n本身唔識既<br />\n而大家又住得都幾近<br />\n所以差唔多日日返學都會撞到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日搭同一架小巴<br />\n<br />\n發現佢份人都幾gentleman <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會做好多我唔expect一個陌生同學會幫我做既野<br />\n例如落車會讓我落先<br />\n知我跟住佢係後面 佢入門口果陣會幫我hold一hold道門咁<br />\n<br />\n慢慢就開始留意多左佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一日撞唔到佢既話會覺得好失落 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf308a8d2fc1c5045f089cb936e439f5a946a655","tid":219821,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:14:09.000Z","msg":"有次跌咗支筆落地 佢幫我執番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果時第一次認真望佢 發覺幾白淨幾瘦<br />\n慢慢我地就一齊咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1815f9b75bfa49161ef6617c05a52ccccdb9071a","tid":219821,"uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:14:16.000Z","msg":"利申 藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545f7a2aaa71ca2e23fc8fb1aad3bd3a96a643ff","tid":219821,"uid":107279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:16:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申 藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差d想講gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cacd0ac9e4cdd521b6717068bfd674c956265749","tid":219821,"uid":107279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:17:01.000Z","msg":"咁你地點開始傾計同抄牌<img sr